                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When the accursed forge-spurned critically hits a target with its soul chain, the chain leeches away a portion of the target's soul. The target must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"36\" data-pf2-traits=\"divine,necromancy\" data-pf2-label=\"Soul Siphon DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save.<br /> <strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.<br /> <strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained} 1. <br /> <strong>Failure</strong> The target is Drained 2.<br /> <strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is Drained 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned} 2 from the pain.</p>"
